g aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 03, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rrf1665702719934.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rrf1665702719934.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rrf1665702719934.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rrf1665702719934\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Check whether the size of the numeric data type falls inside the limits set for the\n      packing code. </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"rrf1665702719934__topic_d142220e1_d142221e1_d142222e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rrf1665702719934__p_d142223e1_d142224e1_d142225e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$NUMERIC_CHECK</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">ON</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">OFF</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rrf1665702719934__section_xpx_ncv_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d611832e68\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"rrf1665702719934__ul_lcn_pcv_jwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rrf1665702719934__li_d50090e1_d50091e1_d50092e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ON</code>—Uniface checks that the value\n               to be stored in the DBMS for a Numeric data type, falls within the upper and lower\n               limit set by the Uniface packing code. If it does not, an error occurs when leaving\n               the field and the data is not stored. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rrf1665702719934__li_d50093e1_d50094e1_d50095e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">OFF</code>—Uniface does not perform the\n               Numeric check. This can cause incorrect data to be stored. Data that falls outside\n               the limits of the Uniface packing code for that field is truncated according to the\n               storage format for the external DBMS connector. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rrf1665702719934__section_wpf_qcv_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d611832e87\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"rrf1665702719934__table_d17066e1_d17067e1_d17068e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Any application assignment file </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS] </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ON</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rrf1665702719934__section_x3p_scv_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d611832e135\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rrf1665702719934__p_d142235e1_d142236e1_d142237e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$NUMERIC_CHECK</span> determines if Uniface checks the limits set by the\n            Uniface packing code before storing a Numeric data type in the DBMS. This check does not\n            apply to data type Float.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rrf1665702719934__p_d142238e1_d142239e1_d142240e1\">When the setting is not present, Uniface behaves as\n            if <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$NUMERIC_CHECK</span> is <code class=\"ph codeph\">ON</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rrf1665702719934__section_wxj_vcv_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d611832e156\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">$NUMERIC_CHECK</code></h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"rrf1665702719934__pre_lxt_wcv_jwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$NUMERIC_CHECK = ON</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531751\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531751\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$NUMERIC_CHECK Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 03, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Check whether the size of the numeric data type falls inside the limits set for the packing code. $NUMERIC_CHECK { = } ON | OFF Arguments ON —Uniface checks that the value to be stored in the DBMS for a Numeric data type, falls within the upper and lower limit set by the Uniface packing code. If it does not, an error occurs when leaving the field and the data is not stored. OFF —Uniface does not perform the Numeric check. This can cause incorrect data to be stored. Data that falls outside the limits of the Uniface packing code for that field is truncated according to the storage format for the external DBMS connector. Defaults Assignment file: Any application assignment file Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: ON Description $NUMERIC_CHECK determines if Uniface checks the limits set by the Uniface packing code before storing a Numeric data type in the DBMS. This check does not apply to data type Float. When the setting is not present, Uniface behaves as if $NUMERIC_CHECK is ON . Example: $NUMERIC_CHECK $NUMERIC_CHECK = ON Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}